            Attenborough agreed with decision to save penguins' lives
            The Dynasties crew took a rare decision to intervene when a group of stranded emperor penguins faced death on the BBC Nature Series.Sir David Attenborough told the executive producer that he would have done the same.Read more: 'Attenborough would have rescued penguins'

                
